    <item>
      <title>拜登寻求保护 90 万移民免受特朗普镇压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/biden-extends-protection-for-800-000-venezuelans-salvadorans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在唐纳德·特朗普就任并誓言打击移民政策的 10 天前，总统乔·拜登的政府延长了对美国境内 60 万委内瑞拉人和 20 多万萨尔瓦多人的临时保护身份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/biden-extends-protection-for-800-000-venezuelans-salvadorans</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 18:08:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为什么拜登告别俄罗斯石油贸易制裁是一件大事</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/why-biden-s-farewell-sanctions-on-russian-oil-are-a-big-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，美国宣布对俄罗斯石油贸易实施迄今为止最全面、最严厉的制裁，而就在十天之前，乔·拜登将离开白宫，由唐纳德·特朗普接任总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/why-biden-s-farewell-sanctions-on-russian-oil-are-a-big-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
